$
  x_1 prime - x_2 prime -x_3 prime-"нормальный вид"\
  mat(x_1; x_2; x_3)= mat(1/5x_1 prime + 2/5x_2 prime-1/5x_3 prime;x_2 prime - x_3 prime;1/3x_3 prime)
$
